code: public static AkkaRpcServiceConfiguration fromConfiguration(Configuration configuration) {     final FiniteDuration duration = AkkaUtils.getTimeout(configuration).     final Time timeout = Time.of(duration.length(), duration.unit()).     final long maximumFramesize = AkkaRpcServiceUtils.extractMaximumFramesize(configuration).     return new AkkaRpcServiceConfiguration(configuration, timeout, maximumFramesize). }
public static AkkaRpcServiceConfiguration defaultConfiguration() {     return fromConfiguration(new Configuration()). }
